wednesday he will proceed with plans to dismantle the justice 
departments organized crime strike forces despite some 
congressional claims the move is unwarranted 
starting jan 1 the 14 strike forces will be folded into 23 
us attorneys offices across the country thornburgh said in a 
statement 
i am convinced that this new organizational structure will not 
only strengthen our efforts against traditional organized criminal 
families but will enhance our efforts against new organized crime 
elements thornburgh said 
