typhoon jack weakened rapidly thursday to 
tropical depression status and no longer posed a threat to this 
us territory or any other islands in the western pacific weather 
officials said 
jacks sustained winds which had been clocked as high as 135 
mph tuesday fell to 30 mph by 11 am thursday according to the 
joint typhoon warning center 
